# Team 1 Portfolio Website

## Project Overview

This project is a collaborative portfolio website created by Team 1.  
The website introduces each team member, highlights their technical skills,
career interests, and provides access to their personal portfolio pages.

The project was developed using:

- HTML
- CSS
- GitHub
- Netlify

---

# Features

- Responsive navigation bar
- Animated gradient background
- Homepage with team overview
- Individual portfolio pages
- Shared CSS styling
- Portfolio links
- GitHub collaboration
- Netlify deployment

---

